To create a React App first start by creating a folder mdkir (name of project) and then in the terminal of that project run npm init -y to create a package.json file.


then run npm install react react-dom react-scripts react-router-dom


you will need public and src folders 

index html will go in the public along with css


in the html file run ! then tab to creae html doc

create a div in the html with a id and a name
react-router-dom

add   "scripts": {
    "start": "react-scripts start",
    "build": "react-scripts build"
  },
